  <entry>
    <title>Hgame2023 week1 WP</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2023/01/09/Hgame2023-week1-WP/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2023/01/09/Hgame2023-week1-WP/</id>
    <published>2023-01-09T03:53:22.380Z</published>
    <updated>2023-01-09T09:06:35.926Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="序言"><a href="#序言" class="headerlink" title="序言"></a>序言</h2><p>寒假没事，前两天打了一下杭电的Hgame，week1挺简单的，把web ak了后又做了两道misc，写一下wp</p><p><img src="/../imgs/Hgame2023-week1-WP/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20230106211633.png" alt="QQ截图20230106211633"></p><h2 id="web"><a href="#web" class="headerlink" title="web"></a>web</h2><h3 id="Classic-Childhood"><a href="#Classic-Childhood" class="headerlink" title="Classic Childhood"></a>Classic Childhood</h3><p>题目介绍是一个纯前端实现的小游戏，那么flag肯定就在源代码里，打开源代码找就行了，其实这题还挺难找的，没有明显的提示。一般来说，肯定是把游戏打通关了会给你一个flag，那直接打开event.js的源码，翻到最底下，发现有四个结局，但是没有一个会给flag，再往下翻，有个a变量，挺长的，是16进制的unicode编码</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function mota() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  var a = [&#x27;\x59\x55\x64\x6b\x61\x47\x4a\x58\x56\x6a\x64\x61\x62\x46\x5a\x31\x59\x6d\x35\x73\x53\x31\x6c\x59\x57\x6d\x68\x6a\x4d\x6b\x35\x35\x59\x56\x68\x43\x4d\x45\x70\x72\x57\x6a\x46\x69\x62\x54\x55\x31\x56\x46\x52\x43\x4d\x46\x6c\x56\x59\x7a\x42\x69\x56\x31\x59\x35&#x27;]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>大差不差就是这个了，直接把 \x 换成 % 后解码，会发现解码后有点像base64，但是base64解出来也并不是flag，多解两次就出来了</p><p><img src="/../imgs/Hgame2023-week1-WP/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20230109110805.png" alt="QQ截图20230109110805"></p><h3 id="Become-A-Member"><a href="#Become-A-Member" class="headerlink" title="Become A Member"></a>Become A Member</h3><p>要用到http知识，进入靶机地址，上来先让提供身份证明</p><p><img src="/../imgs/Hgame2023-week1-WP/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20230109111248.png" alt="QQ截图20230109111248"></p><p>抓个包，身份证明提示 Cute-Bunny</p><p>那把user-agent改为Cute-Bunny</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">User-Agent: Cute-Bunny</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发送过去，会发现给了这样一个回显</p><p><img src="/../imgs/Hgame2023-week1-WP/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20230109111738.png" alt="QQ截图20230109111738"></p><p>响应包里的cookie有个code&#x3D;guest，那很明显了，这里把cookie里的code改为Vidar</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Cookie: code = Vidar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发送，又会得到一个回显</p><p><img src="/../imgs/Hgame2023-week1-WP/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20230109112226.png" alt="QQ截图20230109112226"></p><p>改referer</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Referer: bunnybunnybunny.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后又让改本地请求</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">X-Forwarded-For:127.0.0.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后会给一个账号密码，以json登录就行，这里上网查了才知道，get请求也可以携带body，但是不推荐，害的我改了半天的请求方式，最后的payload</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">GET / HTTP/1.1</span><br><span class="line">Host: week-1.hgame.lwsec.cn:31257</span><br><span class="line">User-Agent: Cute-Bunny</span><br><span class="line">Referer:bunnybunnybunny.com</span><br><span class="line">X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1</span><br><span class="line">Accept: text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,image/avif,image/webp,*/*;q=0.8</span><br><span class="line">Accept-Language: zh-CN,zh;q=0.8,zh-TW;q=0.7,zh-HK;q=0.5,en-US;q=0.3,en;q=0.2</span><br><span class="line">Accept-Encoding: gzip, deflate</span><br><span class="line">Connection: close</span><br><span class="line">Cookie: code=Vidar</span><br><span class="line">Upgrade-Insecure-Requests: 1</span><br><span class="line">Content-Length: 49</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;username&quot;:&quot;luckytoday&quot;,&quot;password&quot;:&quot;happy123&quot;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/../imgs/Hgame2023-week1-WP/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20230109113015.png" alt="QQ截图20230109113015"></p><h3 id="Guess-Who-I-Am"><a href="#Guess-Who-I-Am" class="headerlink" title="Guess Who I Am"></a>Guess Who I Am</h3><p>这题其实只要答对一百分就行了，没什么，题目hint里给了一个github的地址，访问拿到所有人的代号，写个脚本跑一下就行，实在不行一个一个找也可以</p><h3 id="Show-Me-Your-Beauty"><a href="#Show-Me-Your-Beauty" class="headerlink" title="Show Me Your Beauty"></a>Show Me Your Beauty</h3><p>题目让上传头像，先传一个一句话木马上去，抓个包，响应包里有这么一句话</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;&quot;json&quot;:&quot;Invalid File Extension!&quot;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>额外的文件扩展，很明显对文件后缀名进行了过滤，大写Php绕过，上传成功，给了文件上传地址，用蚁剑连一下</p><p><img src="/../imgs/Hgame2023-week1-WP/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20230109113935.png" alt="QQ截图20230109113935"></p><p>在根目录的最底下找到flag</p><h2 id="misc"><a href="#misc" class="headerlink" title="misc"></a>misc</h2><h3 id="e99p1ant-want-girlfriend"><a href="#e99p1ant-want-girlfriend" class="headerlink" title="e99p1ant_want_girlfriend"></a>e99p1ant_want_girlfriend</h3><p>下载题目附件，打开图片是一张自拍，但是图片好像少了一部分，直接用010editor，png.bt分析一下，改一下图片的高度，改为800</p><p><img src="/../imgs/Hgame2023-week1-WP/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20230109114932.png" alt="QQ截图20230109114932"></p><p>flag就出现了<img src="/../imgs/Hgame2023-week1-WP/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20230109115216.png" alt="QQ截图20230109115216"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
